Package: broadlinkac
Version: 3.2-1
Depends: python3-light, python3-broadlink, python3-schedule
Section: utils
Architecture: aarch64_cortex-a53
Maintainer: oywq00008-cell
License: MIT
Description: AI-powered smart AC controller for Broadlink RM series.
 Supports 14 AC brands, dual weather sources (Baidu/QWeather),
 NMC typhoon tracking, auto AC shutdown on storm <100km.
 v3.2: built-in hvac_ir (no pip), device rename, same-model dedup,
  schedule templates with multi-day groups, standalone temp rules.
